story.storyDescription: 213768879: I got the child. Call the father, right now, before he calls the police.
story.title: Wrong Number

messages.text: I got the child. Call the father, right now, before he calls the police.
sorry, you got the wrong number.
ridiculous! Gretchen, I won’t let you duck out.
seriously, stop it. We’re in this together
why are you not picking up?
because I don’t know you and I don’t wanna talk to you!
or maybe because you don’t want me to hear your voice!!
listen, there’s no one here and i don’t know who you’re talking about
I knew something was wrong. I saw how you tried to avoid me today in the office
i don’t think so. I was at lectures all day today
oh yeah? you’ve become a student now?
i am a student, yes. And you’re a fucking weirdo
I don’t know why you’re doing this to me, Gretchen.
leave me alone or i’ll call the police!
hey, I just talked to Gretchen. I got the wrong number. Sorry for bothering you
by the way from those texts I sent you it sounded like I kidnapped someone
just so you know, me and Gretchen are child protection workers.
I believe this little boy is being abused by his dad but because there’s no proof i took him to my house to talk to him in private. We’re not supposed to do that, but I’m worried for him.
i was wondering what you were gonna do to that child
i would NEVER hurt children. They’re my life
well congratulations you’ve got a great job
thanks :) so you’re a student? what do you study?
wow! that’s amazing! you must be really smart ;-)
you could maybe help me then: the little boy has a small burn on his arm. Cigarette
the dad said it was accidental
then it’s probably inflicted. Accidental burns have an indistinct shape
so how are you liking med school?
yes the people are nice! I made lots of friends
that’s good. do you live on campus?
well sorry again for earlier, have a nice evening
i’m so sorry i scared you….
i was so rude. and i’m sure you’re a really nice person
wait a minute, are you chatting me up now???
you can trust me! i told you i’m a good guy
i bet you’re a beautiful girl
no really i’m not that pretty
but i’m sure you’re really smart
i knew it! which medical school do you go to?
i bet it’s like the best in the US
haha yeah its a pretty good one
hey can i ask you something?
i’m not gonna tell you my name!!
oh come on! just your initials? i feel like i know you now ;-) my name is Matthew
haha you’re so weird. my initials are EK
no but i was trying to sleep!!
sorry if i woke you up
i don’t want to pick up i don’t know you
I know, I just want to annoy you
I can’t, I need to find you
Here it is. Room B13. Thanks for letting it ring
there are so many rooms on this campus I wouldn’t have found you otherwise
Did you think I’d let you live after I’d given you all that information about the kidnapping?
you said you were a child protection worker
